      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SOHO PIASTRI (1) made a good return after six months when coming from a wide barrier for second at this circuit and distance last week. Should only be better for that outing and is well served by the inside draw. KIKI MEISTER (9) has worked her way back into form, scoring by 4.2 metres at Penrith last Thursday. Tactics will be crucial from this wider draw but she could go on with it now. YOU ARE MY WISH (4) is racing well, landing a maiden win two back before coming from this barrier to place last week at this circuit and distance. Go well again. THIS IS HEAVEN (7) was last seen when fifth at Listed level five months ago and was a Penrith winner prior. Readied with a trial and owns a decent record at this distance so is well worth keeping safe.",
